  add("EN-E010", "提升", "倒装条件表达理解", "语义选择", "Only after checking the map twice ____ that the marked path was closed.", "直到两次核对地图后，我们才____标记的小路已关闭。", ["we noticed", "did we notice", "we did notice", "noticed we"], 1, W("only+状语置于句首", "主句需部分倒装", "did we notice符合过去时倒装", "only句首触发倒装"), V("Only when the lights went out ____ how quiet the village was.", "直到灯熄灭，我们才____村庄多么安静。", ["we realized", "did we realize", "we did realized", "realized we"], 1));
