  add("EN-E015", "提升", "stop doing/to do辨析", "非谓语语义", "After walking for an hour, the group stopped ____ water and check the route.", "走了一小时后，小组停下来____水并核对路线。", ["drink", "drinking", "to drink", "drank"], 2, W("停止原动作后开始另一动作", "and check与空格并列", "stop to do表示停下来去做", "两动作转换"), V("The librarian asked the boys to stop ____ near the reading area.", "图书管理员让男孩们停止在阅读区附近____。", ["talk", "talking", "to talk", "talked"], 1));
  add("EN-E016", "提升", "对话：建议回应", "补全对话", "A: I often forget new words after a week. B: ____ Try using each word in a sentence of your own.", "A：一周后我常忘记新单词。B：____ 试着用每个词造自己的句子。", ["That's a useful problem.", "Why not review them in context?", "I have never learned words.", "You must stop reading."], 1, W("回应应承接记不住单词的问题", "后句给出语境造句方法", "Why not...构成自然建议", "对话功能"), V("A: I read slowly and often lose the main idea. B: ____ Start by reading the title and the first sentence of each paragraph.", "A：我读得慢且常抓不住主旨。B：____ 先读标题和每段首句。", ["You are certainly right.", "Why not practise finding key information?", "The article is always easy.", "I dislike long passages."], 1));
  add("EN-E017", "提升", "对话：请求澄清", "补全对话", "A: Please hand in the project by next Monday. B: ____ Do you mean before class or by the end of the day?", "A：请下周一前交项目。B：____ 你是指课前还是当天结束前？", ["Could you make that clearer?", "Why are you so late?", "May I borrow your project?", "What a difficult day!"], 0, W("后句询问具体截止时间", "需要先礼貌请求澄清", "Could you make that clearer最衔接", "交际目的"), V("A: Meet me near the west entrance. B: ____ Is that the one beside the bookstore?", "A：在西入口附近见。B：____ 是书店旁那个吗？", ["Could you explain which entrance you mean?", "Would you like another book?", "Why did the store close?", "How long is the meeting?"], 0));
  add("EN-E018", "提升", "对话：表达安慰", "补全对话", "A: I made two mistakes in the final part of the speech. B: ____ You explained the main idea very clearly.", "A：我演讲最后部分犯了两个错误。B：____ 你的主旨解释得很清楚。", ["Never mind. You still did a good job.", "That's why nobody listened.", "You should not speak again.", "The final part was unnecessary."], 0, W("对方因错误沮丧", "后句肯定其主旨表达", "安慰加肯定最符合语境", "情感回应"), V("A: Our model fell apart just before the show. B: ____ You still have time to fix the loose part.", "A：模型展出前散架了。B：____ 你还有时间修松动部分。", ["Don't panic.", "It can never work.", "I told you to stop.", "What a perfect model!"], 0));
  add("EN-E019", "提升", "对话：礼貌拒绝", "补全对话", "A: Could you join our basketball game this afternoon? B: ____ I have promised to help at the library.", "A：今天下午能参加我们的篮球赛吗？B：____ 我答应去图书馆帮忙。", ["I'd love to, but I can't today.", "Of course, the library is closed.", "No, basketball is the best.", "Yes, I dislike helping others."], 0, W("后句给出不能参加的原因", "需要礼貌表达遗憾", "I'd love to, but...符合拒绝功能", "邀请与拒绝"), V("A: Would you like to come to the concert tonight? B: ____ I need to look after my little cousin.", "A：今晚来听音乐会吗？B：____ 我需要照顾小表弟。", ["Thanks, but I'm afraid I can't.", "Certainly, I have no ticket.", "No, the concert sounds wonderful.", "Yes, I will stay at home."], 0));
  add("EN-E020", "提升", "对话：提供帮助", "补全对话", "A: These boxes are too heavy for me. B: ____ We can carry them together.", "A：这些箱子我搬不动。B：____ 我们可以一起搬。", ["Let me give you a hand.", "Please leave them anywhere.", "You should buy more boxes.", "I carried them yesterday."], 0, W("对方遇到搬运困难", "后句提出一起搬", "give you a hand表示主动帮助", "困难与帮助"), V("A: I can't find the data file for our report. B: ____ I saved a copy on the class drive.", "A：我找不到报告数据文件。B：____ 我在班级网盘存了副本。", ["Don't worry. I can help.", "Delete the report now.", "You never need the data.", "The drive is always slow."], 0));
  add("EN-E021", "提升", "对话：确认信息", "补全对话", "A: The train leaves at 7:20, not 7:50. B: ____ I'll change the alarm now.", "A：火车7:20开，不是7:50。B：____ 我现在就改闹钟。", ["Thanks for reminding me.", "That's an interesting train.", "I don't need an alarm.", "You should leave later."], 0, W("对方纠正关键时间", "后句立即修改闹钟", "感谢提醒自然承接", "信息修正后的回应"), V("A: Remember, the meeting is in Room 306. B: ____ I wrote down 360 by mistake.", "A：记住，会议在306室。B：____ 我误写成360了。", ["Good catch, thanks.", "Room 360 is larger.", "I will miss the meeting.", "Why is the room quiet?"], 0));
  add("EN-E022", "提升", "对话：表达观点", "补全对话", "A: Should our school stop selling bottled water? B: ____ Refill stations may be a better first step.", "A：学校应该停止销售瓶装水吗？B：____ 先设置饮水补给站或许更好。", ["I agree with the goal, but we need a practical plan.", "Bottles are made in many colors.", "No student drinks water.", "The station is near the gate."], 0, W("后句提出折中方案", "对目标赞同但关注可行性", "第一项完整表达有保留的观点", "观点与理由"), V("A: Should homework be completed only online? B: ____ Some students may not always have a stable connection.", "A：作业应该只在线完成吗？B：____ 有些学生不一定总有稳定网络。", ["I'm not sure it would be fair to everyone.", "Online work uses a screen.", "Every connection is fast.", "Homework has many subjects."], 0));
  add("EN-E023", "提升", "完形：因果逻辑", "完形填空单空", "Nora noticed that many students left half-full cups after lunch. She placed a small sign beside the bin. ____ fewer drinks were wasted the next day.", "诺拉发现许多学生午饭后留下半杯饮料。她在垃圾桶旁放了小提示牌。____第二天浪费的饮料更少了。", ["However", "As a result", "For example", "At the same time"], 1, W("空格连接措施与变化", "提示牌在前，浪费减少在后", "As a result引出结果", "篇章因果"), V("The class put picture labels on four recycling boxes. ____ even younger students sorted waste correctly.", "全班给四个回收箱贴上图示标签。____连低年级学生也能正确分类。", ["Instead", "As a result", "Otherwise", "In the beginning"], 1));
  add("EN-E024", "提升", "完形：转折逻辑", "完形填空单空", "The first paper bridge looked strong. ____, it broke when we placed the third book on it.", "第一座纸桥看起来很结实。____，放上第三本书时它断了。", ["Besides", "However", "Therefore", "Similarly"], 1, W("外观结实与实际断裂相反", "两句形成明显反差", "However表示转折", "篇章转折"), V("The path seemed shorter on the map. ____, it took us longer because it climbed a steep hill.", "地图上这条路看起来更短。____，因陡坡我们反而走得更久。", ["However", "Therefore", "For example", "Meanwhile"], 0));
